ESS Technology to supply Sony . ESS Technology Inc Wednesday said Sony Corp selected ESS ' MPEG solution for a new video related product . In addition , the company said Eastbase of Hong Kong as well as an affiliate of South Korea ' s LG Group and 16 other Video CD player manufacturers in China , Taiwan , and Hong Kong have selected ESS ' MPEG - 1 decoder solution . ESS also said the company has also shipped half a million units of its ES3204 chip , a highly integrated single - chip MPEG - 1 video , audio , and system decoder ahead of schedule . The milestone was originally targeted for the first quarter of 1997 . ESS designs , develops and markets highly integrated mixed signal semiconductor and software solutions for multimedia applications in the personal computer and consumer marketplaces . 
